</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dtMgUX gYEGeC pf-71_ pf-heading-1-h3"><strong>Engaging in CPD</strong></h3><p class="sc-cZMNgc hqfPHB pf-73_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Participation in CPD programmes ensures that solicitors maintain their knowledge and skills, meeting the Society's standards for professional development.
































